msgstr "[[!pagetemplate template=\"news.tmpl\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"A bunch of people spend a dozen days together in July at the third Tails "
"developers yearly summit. This was a great opportunity to have crazy hacking "
"sessions in person, as well as to discuss where we are heading to and how."
msgstr ""
"Un munt de persones han passat una dotzena de dies juntes al juliol a la "
"tercera cimera anual de desenvolupadors de Tails. Aquesta ha sigut una gran "
"oportunitat per tenir sessions de pirateig boges en persona, així com per "
"discutir cap a on ens dirigim i com."

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Discussions"
msgstr "Debats"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We mainly discussed the **growth of the project**: given the growing number "
"of users and our super-short release cycle, it is a challenge to keep the "
"project sustainable and maintainable in the mid/long term."
msgstr ""
"Vam parlar principalment del **creixement del projecte**: donat el nombre "
"creixent d'usuaris i el nostre cicle de llançament súper curt, és un repte "
"mantenir el projecte sostenible i mantenible a mitjà/llarg termini."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Our take on this is first reflected by our **updated roadmap**: we now have "
"a better vision of what we want to focus on for the next major releases of "
"Tails: the 1.0, 1.1 and 2.0 milestones are now pretty well defined, and we "
"even were bold enough to draft goals for 3.0."
msgstr ""
"La nostra visió d'això es reflecteix primer en el nostre **full de ruta "
"actualitzat**: ara tenim una millor visió del que volem centrar-nos per als "
"propers llançaments importants de Tails: les fites 1.0, 1.1 i 2.0 ara estan "
"força ben definides, i fins i tot vam ser prou atrevits per redactar "
"objectius per a la 3.0."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Another key aspect on this topic was that we need to **make it easier to "
"contribute** to Tails. We have listed many enhancements that could be made "
"in this direction, especially on the website.  We also have identified areas "
"that could benefit most from a few new dedicated contributors. We will "
"publish targeted calls for help in the next few months."
msgstr ""
"Un altre aspecte clau sobre aquest tema és que hem de **facilitar la "
"contribució** a Tails. Hem enumerat moltes millores que es podrien fer en "
"aquesta direcció, especialment al lloc web. També hem identificat àrees que "
"podrien beneficiar-se més d'uns quants nous col·laboradors dedicats. "
"Publicarem crides d'ajuda específiques en els propers mesos."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We also **redesigned our communication channels** to ease involvement of new "
"contributors, to make more workload sharing possible, and to be able to "
"provide better user support. In short:"
msgstr ""
"També hem **redissenyat els nostres canals de comunicació** per facilitar la "
"participació de nous col·laboradors, per fer possible compartir més càrrega "
"de treball i poder oferir un millor suport als usuaris. En resum:"

#. type: Bullet: '  * '
msgid ""
"Our mailing lists see quite a lot of traffic these days.  This might deter "
"people from reading it. So, we will create two specialized mailing lists: a "
"private, encrypted one will receive bug reports, while a public one will be "
"dedicated to user support."
msgstr ""
"Les nostres llistes de correu veuen molt trànsit aquests dies. Això pot "
"dissuadir la gent de llegir-les. Així doncs, crearem dues llistes de correu "
"especialitzades: una privada, encriptada, rebrà informes d'errors, mentre "
"que una de pública estarà dedicada al suport dels usuaris."

#. type: Bullet: '  * '
msgid ""
"A growing FAQ will be assembled: it will be a tool for self-service help, "
"and should make support work less repetitive."
msgstr ""
"Es reunirà una pàgina de preguntes més freqüents creixent: serà una eina "
"d'ajuda d'autoservei i hauria de fer que el treball d'assistència sigui "
"menys repetitiu."

#. type: Bullet: '  * '
msgid ""
"In a few months, we will evaluate how all this fares and we will reconsider "
"web support, which is postponed for the moment."
msgstr ""
"D'aquí a uns mesos, avaluarem com va tot això i reconsiderarem el suport "
"web, que de moment està ajornat."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Still, the tails-dev mailing list remains the main communication channel for "
"development and project-wide discussions."
msgstr ""
"Tot i així, la llista de correu tails-dev continua sent el principal canal "
"de comunicació per al desenvolupament i les discussions a tot el projecte."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This summit gave us the chance to **evaluate and refine processes** that we "
"have set up a year ago, such as our time-based release schedule and a formal "
"merge policy."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta cimera ens va donar l'oportunitat d'**avaluar i perfeccionar els "
"processos** que vam establir fa un any, com ara el nostre programa de "
"llançament basat en el temps i una política formal de fusió."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To end with, the **public development meetings** experiment will be "
"extended, and we will go on having monthly **Low Hanging Fruits sessions**. "
"Not only these sessions are very useful to make Tails better, but we were "
"happy to see new people join these parties recently. We hope to see even "
"more of that in the future: these sessions are great times to **start "
"contributing** to Tails!"
msgstr ""
"Per acabar, s'allargarà l'experiment de les **reunions públiques de "
"desenvolupament** i continuarem fent sessions mensuals de **Low Hanging "
"Fruits**. Aquestes sessions no només són molt útils per millorar Tails, sinó "
"que ens alegra veure que recentment gent nova s'ha incorporat a aquestes "
"festes. Esperem veure-ho encara més en el futur: aquestes sessions són bons "
"moments per **començar a contribuir** a Tails!"

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Hack"
msgstr "Hack"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Hours of meetings were certainly a necessary part of the summit, but we also "
"dedicated a fair share of our time to hands-on activities.  Fortunately "
"there is quite a lot of room for improvements in Tails, so we were never "
"left unoccupied."
msgstr ""
"Certament, les hores de reunions van ser una part necessària de la cimera, "
"però també vam dedicar una bona part del nostre temps a activitats "
"pràctiques. Afortunadament, hi ha molt marge de millora a Tails, de manera "
"que no ens hem quedat desocupats."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The most noticeable technical change that happened during the summit was "
"perhaps our **move to Redmine** for managing our tasks and plans. We are not "
"exploiting the full potential of Redmine yet, but it already feels far less "
"messy than how we did previously. Hopefully this will help others get "
"involved! Many thanks go to Riseup for hosting the Redmine instance we use.  "
"Note that we will keep using ikiwiki for blueprints."
msgstr ""
"El canvi tècnic més notable que s'ha produït durant la cimera ha sigut "
"potser el nostre **canvi a Redmine** per gestionar les nostres tasques i "
"plans. Encara no estem explotant tot el potencial de Redmine, però ja notem "
"que és molt menys desordenat que el mètode anterior. Esperem que això ajudi "
"a altres a participar! Moltes gràcies a Riseup per allotjar la instància de "
"Redmine que fem servir. Tingueu en compte que seguirem utilitzant ikiwiki "
"per als documents de disseny."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Taking advantage of Redmine, we have started classifying tasks in various "
"useful ways: e.g. **easy tickets** do not require much knowledge of the "
"Tails internals to be solved, and are ideal places to get involved. In "
"passing, other nice custom queries provide lists of tasks involving "
"sysadmin.  and web development."
msgstr ""
"Aprofitant Redmine, hem començat a classificar les tasques de diverses "
"maneres útils: per exemple, els **easy tickets** no requereixen gaire "
"coneixement de la part interna de Tails per resoldre's, i són ideals per "
"començar a col·laborar. De passada, altres consultes personalitzades "
"agradables proporcionen llistes de tasques que involucren l'administració de "
"sistemes i el desenvolupament web."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We spent some time listing problems with early builds of **Tails based on "
"Debian Wheezy**. It is now clearer to us what remains to do: [[!tails_ticket "
"6015 desc=\"a few dozens tickets\"]] were created. Did we mention that any "
"kind of help is warmly welcome? :)"
msgstr ""
"Vam passar una estona enumerant problemes amb les primeres versions de "
"**Tails basades en Debian Wheezy**. Ara ens queda més clar què queda per "
"fer: es van crear [[!tails_ticket 6015 desc=\"unes desenes de tiquets\"]]. "
"Hem esmentat que qualsevol tipus d'ajuda és benvinguda? :)"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Our **Jenkins instance** also had been taken care of: it is getting closer "
"to something we can use and rely upon as part of our daily workflow."
msgstr ""
"La nostra **instància de Jenkins** també s'ha atès: s'està apropant a alguna "
"cosa que podem utilitzar i en què podem confiar com a part del nostre flux "
"de treball diari."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"A lot of branches were **merged for the upcoming 0.20 release**, including "
"the installation of Dasher and a first step towards the replacement of "
"TrueCrypt."
msgstr ""
"Es van **fusionar moltes branques per al proper llançament 0.20**, inclosa "
"la instal·lació de Dasher i un primer pas cap a la substitució de TrueCrypt."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The **Pidgin and OTR documentation** was rewritten to be clearer and more "
"precise, as well as our explanation of the way random nicknames are "
"generated for Pidgin accounts."
msgstr ""
"La **documentació de Pidgin i OTR** es va reescriure per ser més clara i "
"precisa, així com la nostra explicació de com es generen els sobrenoms "
"aleatoris per als comptes de Pidgin."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"More steps have also been done towards **not starting Iceweasel** on startup."
msgstr "També s'han fet més passos per **no iniciar Iceweasel** a l'arrencada."

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "At the end is the beginning"
msgstr "Al final és el principi"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"As you can guess, this summit was as intense as the previous ones.  Tails is "
"living decisive times, so we expect the next year to be pretty interesting. "
"*You* can perhaps make the difference, so do not hesitate [[joining the "
"dance|contribute]]!"
msgstr ""
"Com podeu suposar, aquesta cimera va ser tan intensa com les anteriors. "
"Tails viu moments decisius, així que esperem que l'any vinent sigui força "
"interessant. *Tu* potser pots marcar la diferència, així que no dubtis a "
"[[unir-te al ball|contribute]]!"

